title: American Horror Story: Double Feature Season 10 Trailer | Rotten Tomatoes TV
author: Rotten Tomatoes TV
comment: For the first time "LILY RABE" is leading to a season😭😭💕
So glad and excited that Lily and Frances are in this season! And of course Sarah, Evan, Finn, Billie and Leslie❤️

Ok, I'm getting a mix of Misery, with maybe other "I went to a cabin or house to help me write," with Amity Horrorville or any house that makes the man go crazy, and I'm suspecting a little Rosemary's baby.
Chaulkin is perfect casting for the show!
